data.description: Charming Brick Cape Code with first floor bedroom and full bath. There is a Den/Office area when you first enter the home. Kitchen with separate dining area and all newer appliances. Family room with new vinyl plank flooring and fireplace. The second story has two bedrooms and a half bath. Full basement for more family recreation space and large storage area with access to outside. Located close to all the amenities that you could possibly think of including schools, shopping and so much more. The home is being sold AS-IS.
